z.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-publishes-list-of-judicial-candidates-a-year-after-taking-office/0000018c-e032-ddba-abad-e2b3136c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议，呼吁举行选举并罢免内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-calling-for-elections-and-netanyahus-dismissal/0000018c-dfc8-d751-ad8d-ffec1dc00000</link><description>“政府不仅把一箱箱钱交给哈马斯，还一路卖给我们，加沙边境社区的居民。它放弃了我们，他们的谎言于 10 月 7 日在我们脸上爆炸了。”加利·巴苏多 (Gali Basudo) 在特拉维夫集会上说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 19:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-calling-for-elections-and-netanyahus-dismissal/0000018c-dfc8-d751-ad8d-ffec1dc00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡试图推迟以色列国防军调查，以色列国家审计长开始审查军队在加沙战争中的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-tries-to-delay-idf-probe-state-watchdog-begins-review-of-armys-gaza-conduct/0000018c-dfc6-daf6-a5df-dffe871c0000</link><description>国家审计长马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼通知总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府，他将于本周开始审查与战争有关的一系列问题</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 17:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-tries-to-delay-idf-probe-state-watchdog-begins-review-of-armys-gaza-conduct/0000018c-dfc6-daf6-a5df-dffe871c0000</guid></item><item><title>联合国人道主义事务负责人称加沙“不适宜居住”，“饥荒即将来临”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-06/ty-article/un-humanitarian-chief-says-famine-around-the-corner-in-uninhabitable-gaza/0000018c-df45-daf6-a5df-df7dfb880000</link><description>马丁·格里菲斯还警告说，一场迫在眉睫的公共卫生灾难，称加沙仅有的几家部分运转的医院已经不堪重负，物资严重短缺，而医疗设施遭到无情攻击，传染病正在蔓延，</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 15:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-06/ty-article/un-humanitarian-chief-says-famine-around-the-corner-in-